{"tid":954481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜，聖誕節出街逼逼逼 替死咩？？","createTime":"2018-12-24T15:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T15:38:54.000Z","uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2db22691cd58650e7bbcaf0170aa6b37123e2b","tid":954481,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:35:56.000Z","msg":"個個係到逼逼逼，咁夜啲鋪頭都關門啦，唔明出街逼乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收工搭巴士返歸又封晒路，起碼要行半個鐘先有站 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經逼到hihi 啲仆街仲要推架BB車，真係想一腳踢開佢架死人車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶個毛都未生齊嘅BB出嚟替死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">平安夜，聖誕節，除夕出街嘅全部都係食屎狗！情侶就好心留係屋企扑嘢！唔好阻街啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"00a667e658dced599850bf6fbf5531e67c731bf7","tid":954481,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"鬧完啦<br />\n返去打個飛機瞓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f18f9df877c2d94b09b97ba78e1fd38635df2d8","tid":954481,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"特別多港豬鐘意趁墟！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44612f94284c8ef35782d904277dd384527b5e1b","tid":954481,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00a667e658dced599850bf6fbf5531e67c731bf7","tid":954481,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"鬧完啦<br />\n返去打個飛機瞓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class